<br>
Mostly in group, you get invited in group, see only 4 persons including yourself, but the group is full. You can hear the other 2 talk in group, but they do not show in the group window.<br>
<br>
Last night was raid mode that went haywire, we had about 15 people or so in the raid. First group was alltogether, the people in the second group as well, but our group was all scatered. No one in group 3/4/5/6, 1 person in group 7, 2 person in group 8, though those 3 people should have been in the same group.<br>
